"{\"uid\": \"magyarnemzet.hu-english-2024-07-government-reacts-to-scandalous-olympics-opening-ceremony\", \"text\": \"\\\"Imre Madach's London and its phalanstery have moved to Paris,\\\" Balazs Orban commented on last Friday's Olympics opening ceremony that caused outrage among many.  The Hungarian prime minister's policy chief also expressed his displeasure on social media, referencing the 19th century Hungarian writer by posting,  in The Tragedy of Man, one of Hungary's most famous dramas, \\u00a0in scene 11 audiences in London are entertained with scandalous shows.  In the play,\\\"To Adam, who is aghast by the performance, Lucifer - in his mocking way - even praises the show: 'This flame of bacchic fire, that every cheek Suffuses with a rosy shining glow, As though a fond mask on a tear-stained face, Is this not excellent?' Adam. of course, is not impressed by what he is seeing.  One scene later, in the phalanstery, Adam is already lamenting the concept of homeland. In the phalantery portrayed in The Tragedy of Man, nations are being dissolved in the name of progress, and in the London of the piece, decadence is flourishing because of the rampant hedonism.\\\"  Today, Imre Madach's London and its phalanstery have moved to Paris in real life. The opening of the Paris Olympics was not only a show of horrific decadence, it was also a program for the elimination of nations. Two in one - great!  the policy director commented with irony, adding that the opening ceremony of the Olympic Games is traditionally the event in which every nation shows the world who they are, what they think, what their values are and what they bring to the whole. \\\"Obviously, it cannot be said that the whole French nation agrees with what we have just seen. But one can say that this is what the French liberal elite thinks about their own nation - above all, that it no longer exists. Naturally, every nation is entitled to think what it wants about itself, its future and its place in the world. It also has the right to share it with a wide audience,\\\" the politician stressed.        At the same time, Balazs Orban also stressed that there is only one danger: that what we saw on Friday is not just a one-off phenomenon, but the agenda of the current liberal Western world.  \\\"This is how they want us Hungarians to live, and how they want everyone to live as people of the new ideas. Anyone who doubts this should take a look at the reasons why the European Union and its relevant bodies are exerting monetizable pressure on Hungary, especially because of the Child Protection Act and the anti-migration measures.  Not without reason. From this point of view, it is understandable why many in Hungary are demanding an 18+ age restriction be put on video of the opening ceremony. But even without an advisory legal warning, the vast majority of Hungarians still stand on the ground of common sense. For us, being Hungarian, belonging to the nation is the program, \\u00a0the program for our common development - not the kitsch we see on TV.\\\"  That is why he is repulsed by the Paris phalanstery and this pervasive liberal decadence. Proving that there still exists a nation in this homeland,  the policy chief concluded the post.      The government has repeatedly signaled that it is ready to help.  A carbon tax would be imposed on households.  The EU is no longer an actor in global politics, said Peter Szijarto, sharply criticizing Brussels.  The latest polling also shows that only three parties would enter parliament.  \\u00d6sszesen 0 komment  A kommentek nem szerkesztett tartalmak, tartalmuk a szerz\\u0151j\\u00fck \\u00e1ll\\u00e1spontj\\u00e1t t\\u00fckr\\u00f6zi. Miel\\u0151tt hozz\\u00e1sz\\u00f3lna, k\\u00e9rj\\u00fck, olvassa el akommentszab\\u00e1lyzatot.  Jelenleg csak a hozz\\u00e1sz\\u00f3l\\u00e1sok egy kis r\\u00e9sz\\u00e9t l\\u00e1tja. Hozz\\u00e1sz\\u00f3l\\u00e1shoz \\u00e9s a tov\\u00e1bbi kommentek megtekint\\u00e9s\\u00e9hez l\\u00e9pjen be, vagy regisztr\\u00e1ljon!  The government has repeatedly signaled that it is ready to help.  A carbon tax would be imposed on households.  The EU is no longer an actor in global politics, said Peter Szijarto, sharply criticizing Brussels.  The latest polling also shows that only three parties would enter parliament.  A magyar sz\\u00f6vets\\u00e9g szektorbez\\u00e1r\\u00e1ssal s\\u00fajtotta a klubot.  \\u201eAzt hitt\\u00fck, van vissza\\u00fat\\\" - megsz\\u00f3lalt a sz\\u00ednm\\u0171v\\u00e9sz any\\u00f3sa, Dallos Szilvia.  A Tisza P\\u00e1rt eln\\u00f6k\\u00e9nek a talpa alatt egyre forr\\u00f3bb a talaj.  Eld\\u0151lt, hogy a vil\\u00e1gbajnoks\\u00e1g k\\u00f6z\\u00e9pd\\u00f6nt\\u0151j\\u00e9ben magyar-rom\\u00e1n rangad\\u00f3t is rendeznek.  A magyar v\\u00e1logatottat is keser\\u00edt\\u0151 rom\\u00e1n sikerkapit\\u00e1ny s\\u00falyos v\\u00e1dakkal n\\u00e9z szembe.  Ett\\u0151l az eg\\u00e9sz Tisza P\\u00e1rt megrogyott.  A Liverpool megszak\\u00edtotta a veres\\u00e9gsorozat\\u00e1t a Liverpool otthon\\u00e1ban.  \\u00d6sszess\\u00e9g\\u00e9ben azonban a magyar v\\u00e1logatott csapatkapit\\u00e1nya viszi el a p\\u00e1lm\\u00e1t.  A f\\u0151polg\\u00e1rmesternek a Budapest Brand-botr\\u00e1ny miatt is f\\u0151het a feje.  A Magyar Nemzet k\\u00f6z\\u00e9leti napilap konzervat\\u00edv, nemzeti alapr\\u00f3l, a t\\u00e9nyekre \\u00e9p\\u00edtve adja k\\u00f6zre a legfontosabb t\\u00e1rsadalmi, politikai, gazdas\\u00e1gi, kultur\\u00e1lis \\u00e9s sport t\\u00e9m\\u00e1j\\u00fa inform\\u00e1ci\\u00f3kat.  A program Br\\u00fcsszel h\\u00e1bor\\u00fas terveit finansz\\u00edrozn\\u00e1.  Nagy brav\\u00far volt!  Egyre t\\u00f6bb inform\\u00e1ci\\u00f3 utal arra, hogy a Tisza P\\u00e1rt k\\u00f6r\\u00fcl olyan ukr\\u00e1n \\u00fczleti \\u00e9s civil kapcsolatok jelentek meg, amelyek Ruszin-Szendi Romulusz rokon\\u00e1hoz \\u00e9s nemzetk\\u00f6zi \\u00e9rdekk\\u00f6r\\u00f6kh\\u00f6z k\\u00f6thet\\u0151k.  Mindm\\u00e1ig sok r\\u00e1galom, hazugs\\u00e1g jelenik meg a p\\u00fcsp\\u00f6kr\\u0151l.  Szijj\\u00e1rt\\u00f3 P\\u00e9ter az orsz\\u00e1gj\\u00e1r\\u00e1s\\u00e1n tartott lakoss\\u00e1gi f\\u00f3rumon hangs\\u00falyozta, hogy a br\\u00fcsszeli vezet\\u0151k a h\\u00e1bor\\u00fa meghosszabb\\u00edt\\u00e1s\\u00e1n dolgoznak.  A rend\\u0151rs\\u00e9g az adventi id\\u0151szak kezdet\\u00e9vel orsz\\u00e1gszerte fegyveres, goly\\u00f3\\u00e1ll\\u00f3 mell\\u00e9nyekkel felszerelt j\\u00e1r\\u0151r\\u00f6ket \\u00e1ll\\u00edtott szolg\\u00e1latba.  \\u00daj dr\\u00f3nelh\\u00e1r\\u00edt\\u00f3 egys\\u00e9g j\\u00f6n l\\u00e9tre.  Allahu akbar!  Az angol sajt\\u00f3ban ism\\u00e9t a Fradi h\\u00fasz\\u00e9ves k\\u00f6z\\u00e9pp\\u00e1ly\\u00e1s\\u00e1nak nev\\u00e9t lehet olvasni.  Vicces Facebook-bejegyz\\u00e9snek indult, azt\\u00e1n valami eg\\u00e9szen m\\u00e1s lett bel\\u0151le.  Az e heti telihold m\\u00e1s lesz, mint a t\\u00f6bbi.  A Magyar Nemzet k\\u00f6z\\u00e9leti napilap konzervat\\u00edv, nemzeti alapr\\u00f3l, a t\\u00e9nyekre \\u00e9p\\u00edtve adja k\\u00f6zre a legfontosabb t\\u00e1rsadalmi, politikai, gazdas\\u00e1gi, kultur\\u00e1lis \\u00e9s sport t\\u00e9m\\u00e1j\\u00fa inform\\u00e1ci\\u00f3kat.  Ne maradjon le a Magyar Nemzet legjobb \\u00edr\\u00e1sair\\u00f3l, olvassa \\u0151ket mindennap!  Portf\\u00f3li\\u00f3nk min\\u0151s\\u00e9gi tartalmat jelent minden olvas\\u00f3 sz\\u00e1m\\u00e1ra. Egyed\\u00fcl\\u00e1ll\\u00f3 el\\u00e9r\\u00e9st, orsz\\u00e1gos lefedetts\\u00e9get \\u00e9s v\\u00e1ltozatos megjelen\\u00e9si lehet\\u0151s\\u00e9get biztos\\u00edt. Folyamatosan keress\\u00fck az \\u00faj ir\\u00e1nyokat \\u00e9s fejl\\u0151d\\u00e9si lehet\\u0151s\\u00e9geket. Ez j\\u00f6v\\u0151nk z\\u00e1loga.\"}"